highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “Golden” is the highest at #15.
“Sequência da Botação” by DJ Ryder, Dj Dudu Coupper, and Mc Gw is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #50.
“Ara Beni Lütfen” by Kenan Doğulu has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 86 days straight.
“Valentino” by MC Willian, DJ Japa NK, and DJ DAVI DOGDOG is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 14 spots at #85.
